videos.headline: Georgia State strikes first on Gentry's TD
videos.description: Dan Ellington hits Devin Gentry for the wide receiver's first score of the season to put Georgia State on top of Appalachian State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia State strikes first on Gentry's TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Thomas squeezes a TD pass into Sutton
videos.description: Zac Thomas fires a 12-yard touchdown pass to Corey Sutton to draw Appalachian State even with Georgia State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thomas squeezes a TD pass into Sutton) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Bacon jumps route for sizzling Georgia State pick-6
videos.description: Zac Thomas' pass is intercepted by Chris Bacon and he takes it to the end zone for a Georgia State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bacon jumps route for sizzling Georgia State pick-6) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Evans lands on defender, gets up for 29-yard touchdown
videos.description: Darrynton Evans lands on a defender, but is never down and rises to his feet and runs to the end zone for a 29-yard Appalachian State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Evans lands on defender, gets up for 29-yard touchdown) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Sutton makes incredible circus catch from the ground
videos.description: Corey Sutton has the ball bounce off his body several times before popping back up to him for the deep reception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sutton makes incredible circus catch from the ground) 2019/11/16
